# research_agent inherits GROQ_API_KEY, GROQ_MODEL, SUPABASE_URL, and
# SUPABASE_KEY automatically from the shared ../.env (see that file
# for setup). Nothing needs to be repeated here unless this specific
# project needs a different value than the rest of the system.
# Uncomment and set only what should genuinely differ here, for
# example a faster, smaller model just for research queries:

# GROQ_MODEL=groq/llama-3.1-8b-instant
